      "options": {
        "content": "<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; min-height: 480px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #1a1d24 0%, #0e1014 100%); padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #2d3139;\">\n  <h1 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\">JAULA DE ELEVACIÓN</h1>\n  <p style=\"color: #8e96a5; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 48px; text-align: center; max-width: 600px;\">Seleccione uno de los módulos principales para acceder al panel correspondiente.</p>\n  \n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 24px; width: 100%; max-width: 1400px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n    <a href=\"/d/panel-oee-mes-fabrica\" style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 280px; min-width: 240px; text-decoration: none;\">\n      <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.08) 0%, rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.03) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.35); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\"\n           onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.8)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.2)';\" \n           onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(37, 201, 214, 0.35)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)';\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #25C9D6;\">📊</div>\n        <h2 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">OEE / MES</h2>\n        <p style=\"color: #a2aab7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.45;\">Indicadores OEE en tiempo real, tasas de disponibilidad, rendimiento, calidad y estado de máquina.</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n    \n    <a href=\"/d/mes-plan-v1\" style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 280px; min-width: 240px; text-decoration: none;\">\n      <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08) 0%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.03) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.35); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\"\n           onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.8)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2)';\" \n           onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.35)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)';\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #a855f7;\">📋</div>\n        <h2 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">PLAN PRODUCCIÓN</h2>\n        <p style=\"color: #a2aab7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.45;\">Seguimiento en tiempo real del plan de producción frente a secuencias reales finalizadas.</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a href=\"/d/mes-oee-v2\" style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 280px; min-width: 240px; text-decoration: none;\">\n      <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.08) 0%, rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.03) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.35); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\"\n           onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.8)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.2)';\" \n           onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.35)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)';\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #FFA500;\">🔧</div>\n        <h2 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">DISTRIBUIDOR</h2>\n        <p style=\"color: #a2aab7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.45;\">Tiempos de elevación y descenso del distribuidor hidráulico, con y sin carga.</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a href=\"/d/mes-reg-v1\" style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 280px; min-width: 240px; text-decoration: none;\">\n      <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.08) 0%, rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.03) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.35); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\"\n           onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.8)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.2)';\" \n           onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(47, 208, 106, 0.35)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)';\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #2FD06A;\">⚙️</div>\n        <h2 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">LOG SECUENCIAS</h2>\n        <p style=\"color: #a2aab7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.45;\">Historial de pruebas, tiempos y márgenes de elevación y descenso con detalle por modelo.</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a href=\"/d/mes-alarms-v1\" style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 280px; min-width: 240px; text-decoration: none;\">\n      <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.08) 0%, rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.03) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.35); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\"\n           onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.8)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.2)';\" \n           onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(227, 38, 54, 0.35)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)';\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #E32636;\">🚨</div>\n        <h2 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">ALARMAS</h2>\n        <p style=\"color: #a2aab7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.45;\">Monitoreo en tiempo real de alarmas activas, advertencias del sistema e historial detallado de incidencias.</p>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
